readable.content: Three dogs are running side by side on the grass . Three dogs , one Rottweiler with a tennis ball in its mouth , one Irish Setter and one Corgi are running in field . Three dogs running in a field . Three dogs trot on a stretch of grass , and one dog is carrying a tennis ball . Three dogs with tongues out running on the grass with a tennis ball .
